OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,FA pub landlord from Wokingham says his
OL,7,Fpub is under threat because of ongoing
OL,8,Froadworks outside his front door.
OL,10,FTom McNelly runs the White Horse Pub
OL,11,Fand says his business is suffering due
OL,12,Fto the works taking place on
OL,13,FEasthampstead Road.
OL,15,FWokingham Borough Council is carrying
OL,16,Fout major works as part of efforts to
OL,17,Faccommodate more housing in the area.
OL,19,FBut Mr McNelly and other business
OL,20,Fowners say the diversions are driving
OL,21,Fcustomers away.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
