PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian he said that
OL,7,Fthe pub is losing around #5000 every
OL,8,Fweek because of a fall in trade due to
OL,9,Fthe roadworks.
OL,11,F"It's getting to the stage now where
OL,12,Fwe've sort of handed our notice in,"
OL,13,FMr McNelly said.
OL,15,F"We're not getting people through the
OL,16,Fdoor like we used to.
OL,18,F"People think the road's just
OL,19,Fcompletely shut, the pub's shut.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,F"We've put everything out on social
OL,7,Fmedia, papers, just saying, well,
OL,8,Fwe're still open, but people are just
OL,9,Fgetting all confused with road signs
OL,10,Fand blockages. (
OL,12,F"We've been here quite a while and put
OL,13,Fa lot of effort and time into the
OL,14,Fplace to rebuild it from where we took
OL,15,Fover from.
OL,17,F"And then it's taken probably a month
OL,18,Ffor it just to be shut down by
OL,19,Froadworks and signage, mainly.
OL,21,F"It's just not helped at all."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
