FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,FAfter 10 years of running the pub Tom
OL,7,Fsays it's no longer financially viable.
OL,9,FHe added that the pub only took #150
OL,10,Fon Easter Saturday when he'd normally
OL,11,Fexpect to be extremely busy.
OL,13,FGayle Sharples owns Enchanting Glass
OL,14,FDesigns and says her business is also
OL,15,Ffeeling the impact of the roadworks.
OL,17,F"Unfortunately, it's not great at
OL,18,Fall," she said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,F"The other Friday, I actually took #4
OL,7,Fon a day when I should be taking more
OL,8,Flike #700.
OL,10,F"I keep hoping that the roads and
OL,11,Fpeople will learn to do the diversion
OL,12,Fa little bit differently, but it's too
OL,13,Ffar.
OL,15,F"I think with the cost of fuel having
OL,16,Fgone up so much as well now, that's
OL,17,Feven impacting us even more."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
