PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,FA Wokingham Borough Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The new South
OL,8,FWokingham Distributor Road is a major
OL,9,Fdevelopment to accommodate part of the
OL,10,Fgovernment's target for new housing in
OL,11,FWokingham Borough.
OL,13,F"The plan to close Easthampstead Road,
OL,14,Fwhich is crossed by the new main road,
OL,15,Fwas approved in 2021.
OL,17,F"We appreciate the challenges that all
OL,18,Fbusiness face in the current
OL,19,Fenvironment and the additional
OL,20,Fpressures which roadworks can cause.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,F"We have worked closely with local
OL,7,Fbusinesses throughout this project to
OL,8,Fshare information and we are able to
OL,9,Foffer advice about the support
OL,10,Favailable to those experiencing
OL,11,Fhardship.
OL,13,F"Access to businesses is being
OL,14,Fmaintained throughout the project, but
OL,15,Fwith some diversions required whilst
OL,16,Fexisting roads and junctions are
OL,17,Fadapted to accommodate the new road.
OL,19,F"We've also shared information
OL,20,Fregularly with residents to advise on
OL,21,Fthe best way to reach these businesses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775725560
OL,3,CPub landlord losing thousands every
OL,4,Cweek in trade because of roadworks
OL,6,F"We are working hard to ensure that
OL,7,Fthe project is delivered as soon as
OL,8,Fpossible to enable traffic to flow
OL,9,Ffreely again and for the new houses to
OL,10,Fbe occupied to bring in new customers
OL,11,Ffor our great local businesses."
